### Critical Fix Applied

**`apps/web/eslint.config.mjs` (new file)** — The shared ESLint config was defined but never consumed. Without this file, `next lint` had no way to discover the `@repo/no-hardcoded-colors` rule. Verified the rule now fires correctly on TSX files with hardcoded hex colors in className/style attributes.

